entries.journal_entry_description: A Gungan artifact was stolen by the Maulers. Get it back.
entries.journal_entry_title: Recover the Gungan artifact stolen by the Maulers.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: The Maulers have one of the stolen Gungan artifacts. Assault their bunker so that you'll have a chance to get it back.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Da Mauler master in da bunker bein' Driton Fitch. More dan likely, he'll have da artifact.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Defeat Driton Fitch, a Mauler master and leader of this group of Maulers. He will probably have the stolen artifact.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Defeat Driton Fitch, a Mauler master
entries.task04_comm_message_text: Driton didn't have da artifact. Search da bunker. It must be dere somewhere.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: The Mauler leader, Driton Fitch, didn't have the artifact, so it must be somewhere in the bunker.
entries.task05_journal_entry_title: Find the Gungan Artifact in the Mauler Camp
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Your assault on the Maulers continues.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Fight your way into the Mauler bunker.
